hi\u1ec7n xuy&ecirc;n su\u1ed1t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed h&igrave;nh th&agrave;nh ph&aacute;t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a C&ocirc;ng ty C\u1ed5 Ph\u1ea7n Hichem Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1. Quy \u0111\u1ecbnh th&ocirc;ng tin c&aacute; nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thu th\u1eadp b\u1edfi Hichemvn.com<\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">- Hichemvn.com s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th&ocirc;ng tin thu th\u1eadp t\u1eeb kh&aacute;ch v&atilde;ng lai v&agrave; kh&aacute;ch \u0111&atilde; \u0111\u0103ng k&yacute; l&agrave; \u0111\u1ea1i l&yacute;, th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n website Hichemvn.com \u0111\u1ec3 ph&aacute;t tri\u1ec3n website ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng phong ph&uacute; h\u01a1n, ph&ugrave; h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch h\u01a1n. Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i thu th\u1eadp c&aacute;c lo\u1ea1i th&ocirc;ng tin sau:<\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">- Th&ocirc;ng tin Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch cung c\u1ea5p cho ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i: Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i thu th\u1eadp th&ocirc;ng tin c&aacute; nh&acirc;n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p b\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trang web. &quot;Th&ocirc;ng tin c&aacute; nh&acirc;n&quot; bao g\u1ed3m t&ecirc;n, \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9, s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 email, ng&agrave;y sinh, \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 IP.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">- Th&ocirc;ng tin c&aacute; nh&acirc;n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thu th\u1eadp khi qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch \u0111\u0103ng k&yacute; m\u1ed9t t&agrave;i kho\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i trang web Hichemvn.com, \u0111\u1eb7t h&agrave;ng tr&ecirc;n website, tham gia nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c thi do ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c th&ocirc;ng qua website Hichemvn.com, tham d\u1ef1 r&uacute;t th\u0103m tr&uacute;ng th\u01b0\u1edfng ho\u1eb7c tham gia c&aacute;c kh\u1ea3o s&aacute;t, ho\u1eb7c khi qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch giao ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn n&agrave;o c\u1ee7a ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i nh\u01b0 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u0103m s&oacute;c kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng, t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n, b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng ho\u1eb7c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt th&ocirc;ng qua trang web, \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, email, th\u01b0 t&iacute;n ho\u1eb7c fax. Trong m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i c&oacute; th\u1ec3 c&oacute; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t&ecirc;n v&agrave; \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 email c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh&aacute;c m&agrave; qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ec3 chia s\u1ebb th&ocirc;ng tin tr&ecirc;n website Hichemvn.com.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">- Web Beacons: Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i c&oacute; th\u1ec3 thu th\u1eadp th&ocirc;ng tin ng\u01b0\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng t\u1eeb website th&ocirc;ng qua vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng &quot;Web Beacons&quot;. Web Beacons l&agrave; nh\u1eefng trang web s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c&ocirc;ng ngh\u1ec7 cookie cho ph&eacute;p ghi l\u1ea1i d\u1eef li\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 truy c\u1eadp ho\u1eb7c c&aacute;c giao d\u1ecbch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n tr&ecirc;n website, v&iacute; d\u1ee5: l\u01b0\u1ee3t truy c\u1eadp v&agrave;o c&aacute;c m\u1ee5c ho\u1eb7c c&aacute;c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, th&aacute;i \u0111\u1ed9 \u01b0a th&iacute;ch, quan t&acirc;m d&ograve;ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n&agrave;o&hellip;.Nh\u1eefng th&ocirc;ng tin ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i thu th\u1eadp kh&ocirc;ng li&ecirc;n quan g&igrave; \u0111\u1ebfn th&ocirc;ng tin c&aacute; nh&acirc;n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. C&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng s\u1ed1 n&agrave;y ch\u1ec9 d&ugrave;ng \u0111\u1ec3 theo d&otilde;i v&agrave; c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a trang web, nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n v&agrave; s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ec5 d&agrave;ng h\u01a1n cho qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch v&agrave; c&aacute;c kh&aacute;ch truy c\u1eadp kh&aacute;c.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">- Cookies: Th&ocirc;ng qua vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Cookies, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i thu th\u1eadp v&agrave; ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 IP \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1ed1i k\u1ebft m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh c\u1ee7a qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch v\u1edbi internet; m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh v&agrave; th&ocirc;ng tin k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i nh\u01b0 tr&igrave;nh duy\u1ec7t v&agrave; phi&ecirc;n b\u1ea3n tr&igrave;nh duy\u1ec7t; h\u1ec7 \u0111i\u1ec1u h&agrave;nh; l\u1ecbch s\u1eed mua h&agrave;ng; x&aacute;c nh\u1eadn khi qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch m\u1edf email m&agrave; ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i g\u1eedi cho qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch; ng&agrave;y gi\u1edd v&agrave; c&aacute;c URL \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi website ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i. Cookie kh&ocirc;ng th\u1ec3 truy c\u1eadp ho\u1eb7c ph&acirc;n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1eef li\u1ec7u trong \u1ed5 c\u1ee9ng m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh c\u1ee7a qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch. Th&ocirc;ng th\u01b0\u1eddng qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp tr&igrave;nh duy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 v&ocirc; hi\u1ec7u h&oacute;a cookie hay th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o cho qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch bi\u1ebft khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi cookie.Hi\u1ec7n nay tr&ecirc;n th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169ng c&oacute; s\u1eb5n c&aacute;c ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m cho ph&eacute;p qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch truy c\u1eadp v&agrave;o trang web m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c\u1ea7n cung c\u1ea5p th&ocirc;ng tin n&agrave;y. Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch&agrave;o \u0111&oacute;n \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ebfng th\u0103m Hichemvn.com khi qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, nh\u01b0ng ch&uacute;ng t&o